        <div class="title">
          <span>I want to visit specific locations on my expedition, can this be guaranteed?</span>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
          <p>
            Unfortunately not, all of our expedition voyages and lodges are expeditionary in nature. As they operate in the remotest of regions, they must take into account the conditions of each day/hour.
          </p>
          <p>
            You can be assured that our expedition teams are of the highest calibre and make expert decisions, with the group's best interest and safety at the forefront of their decision making process. Sometimes, this does mean that highlights of expeditions, maybe missed if the conditions do not allow for it.
          </p>
          <p>
            Ultimately, our operators place complete faith in their expedition leaders and team and the expedition follows their command.
          </p>
        </div>
