          <span>Is there a doctor on the expedition?</span>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
          <p>
            Yes, it a requirement of all expedition vessels to travel with a qualified medical doctor on board. The doctor on board, will operate a small, but well equipped infirmary. The ship doctor will be introduced to you on board and you will be made well aware of the location of the infirmary
          </p>
        </div>
